public abstract class BaseCollection<Value> extends Object implements com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Addable<Value>, Collection<Value>, Countable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Joinable<Value>, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Sequence<Value>, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Sized, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.StringFormattable
Base class for all KivaKit collections.

A set with a maximum size. Adds useful methods to the usual Set operations, as well as implementing:

  • Addable
  • Collection
  • Countable
  • Joinable
  • Sequence
  • Sized
  • Joinable
  • StringFormattable
